class="formatted"><div
class="simplesocialbuttons"><div
class="simplesocialbutton ssb-buttom-twitter"><a
href="https://twitter.com/share" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','twitter.com']);" class="twitter-share-button" data-text="Metro de Nueva York" data-url="http://www.newyorkando.com/transporte/metro-de-nueva-york" rel="nofollow"></a></div><div
